data.description: Boise Idaho Home for sale! Charter Pointe offers a community pool, gym, and huge park! The home is close to shopping, golf courses, and schools! This home's floor plan has an open living room to a tiled dining area and kitchen. The kitchen has plenty of cabinetry, lots of counter space, full tiled backsplash and a large pantry. Spacious bedrooms with 2 full bathrooms upstairs and a 1/2 bath downstairs. The master bedroom has a walk in closet. Large fully fenced yard with no rear neighbors! This Boise Idaho home is ready for a new homeowner!
